# in __main__ block:
#
# All tests use the full pipeline:
#   WithDenseView(StMoeModule(exp))(st_attention(input, mask))
# Every test hits the LLM via st_moe forward.
# WithDenseView handles sparse↔dense conversion around StMoe.
#
# ── Forward: WithDenseView(StMoe)(st_attention(x)) ──
#
# 1. shape 1x3 causal: output shape == input shape, all elements non-None
# 2. output is LLM-generated: output text differs from raw input
# 3. full attention 1x3: all positions see all tokens, output valid
# 4. diagonal 1x3: self-only → plain-like input, moe still produces output
# 5. causal 1x5: all 5 outputs non-None
# 6. padding 1x4 (2 real + 2 pad): WithDenseView strips pads,
#    StMoe only processes real tokens, result sparse has 2 elements
# 7. multi-batch 2x3 causal: independent pipelines per batch
# 8. different masks same input: causal vs full → different outputs
# 9. storage consistency: coeff-storage invariant on output
# 10. get_causal_attention_mask integration: end-to-end with mask utility
# 11. sliding window 1x4: non-causal mask, all outputs valid
# 12. large batch 3x4 causal: stress test, no crash, all non-None
#
# ── Backward ──
#
# 13. backward shape: grad flows through WithDenseView + StMoe + st_attention
# 14. backward grad_input shape: grad shape matches input
# 15. grad_experience shape
# 16. multi-batch 2x2 backward
#
# ── End-to-end ──
#
# 17. two-iteration training loop: loop completes, both outputs non-None
# 18. experience update: experience entries modified after training
